Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.33,0:00:04.94,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Ladies and gentlemen,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.94,0:00:08.16,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I bring you marvelous illusions that \Nmake this town sparkle at night!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.16,0:00:12.49,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Please enjoy the miracle that happens \Naround a stage heroine tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.17,0:00:21.16,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,1)}Marth and Rosa
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.62,0:00:21.16,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone! This theater \Nfinally opens tomorrow!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.16,0:00:26.17,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's also opening day for {\i1}Marth and Rosa{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.45,0:00:32.30,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the day our mortal enemy, Kid the \NPhantom Thief, says he's going to appear!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.30,0:00:37.80,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Our duty this time is to protect \Nthe world's largest emerald,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.62,0:00:44.81,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Green Dream, as it's being used \Nfor tomorrow's performance only!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.81,0:00:47.81,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.17,0:00:51.81,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't let your guard down, \Neven among fellow officers.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.49,0:00:56.21,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He's a master of disguise!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.21,0:01:01.96,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He may already be here right now, \Nposing as one of us!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.83,0:01:06.83,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, part-timer! A little help over here!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.92,0:01:08.83,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.39,0:01:14.34,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,All right! I'm going to deploy you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.64,0:01:19.68,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Teams 1 and 2 take the first floor \Nfront lobby and the lobby gallery.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.58,0:01:24.35,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,How many officers did you bring here, \NInspector Nakamori?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.02,0:01:31.48,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But that suits \NKid the Phantom Thief just fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.50,0:01:29.47,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Team 3, the 4th-floor lounge. \NTeams 4 and 5, the fountain plaza.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.48,0:01:34.27,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, give me a break!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.65,0:01:38.66,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't even get through these short lines?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.66,0:01:40.37,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.37,0:01:44.52,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you trying to disgrace my \Nperformance with your lousy acting?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.52,0:01:46.75,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,N-No, I would never...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.75,0:01:51.88,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Reiko. Megumi-chan isn't \Nused to being on stage yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.88,0:01:53.55,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't need to get that mad.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.84,0:01:56.49,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You're just as bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.49,0:01:59.30,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though you're playing the prince, \Nyou fumble your lines.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.30,0:02:02.56,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's only when you throw in \Ntoo many ad libs!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.56,0:02:04.24,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.24,0:02:06.24,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the heroine.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.24,0:02:08.81,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,All of you should just focus on \Nmaking me look good.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.17,0:02:12.31,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Or rather, the tour de force \Nof Imaizumi Reiko!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.69,0:02:20.06,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems further rehearsing \Nwouldn't do any good.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.06,0:02:21.32,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going home.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.84,0:02:25.78,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll leave the rest to you, fearless leader.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.78,0:02:28.33,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hey, Reiko-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.33,0:02:30.44,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,P-Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.39,0:02:34.28,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't mess up anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.28,0:02:36.09,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I promise I'll do my best,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.65,0:02:38.09,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,so please, let's practice once more!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.52,0:02:43.35,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You're Furuhata Megumi-san, I believe?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.35,0:02:45.18,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.40,0:02:49.48,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You have no talent.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.23,0:02:53.29,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't be an actress.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.29,0:02:55.73,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It'd be better if you gave it up now.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.73,0:02:57.56,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Reiko!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.15,0:03:03.74,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sheesh. What a diva.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.22,0:03:06.38,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Who is she?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.38,0:03:09.25,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The daughter of this theater's owner.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.55,0:03:14.51,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though she used her parent's pull to \Nland that part, she lords it over everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.51,0:03:18.21,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,When I think that she's the heroine, \Nit makes me want to take up a different trade.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.60,0:03:24.14,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I hope Kid the Phantom Thief \Nwrecks the whole show.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.95,0:05:11.95,Signs - Thief Title,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1000,0)}Green Dream
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.95,0:05:15.96,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,Marth and Roza\N0 days until the show opens
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.42,0:05:13.85,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Good job, everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.85,0:05:15.96,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Good job!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.96,0:05:19.80,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, kid! You wanna go out drinking with us?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.80,0:05:22.46,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I've still got a few...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.45,0:05:25.47,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,...tricks to prepare for tomorrow!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.47,0:05:27.97,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9}Electric Room
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.47,0:05:34.73,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That being said, with all the cops around,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.73,0:05:36.48,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't do what I need to!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.98,0:05:38.98,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a pretty pickle!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.62,0:05:44.34,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Marth-sama, Marth-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.98,0:05:44.99,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,Main Hall Stage Entrance
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.99,0:05:51.99,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Whither are you, Marth-sama?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.99,0:05:55.34,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Please, throw that name away right now...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.68,0:05:56.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Who's here this late?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.00,0:06:01.50,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Okay. If that is your wish, \NI'll be happy to dispose of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.88,0:06:06.51,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Oh! Marth-sama! What are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.51,0:06:08.06,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Why did you come?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.06,0:06:11.51,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}If you're found here, \Nyou're as good as dead...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.51,0:06:16.02,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the girl who got chewed out \Nbefore during rehearsal...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.51,0:06:16.02,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Oh, no! My father's here!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.02,0:06:18.56,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,W-Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.02,0:06:19.92,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Who are you?! Get him!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.56,0:06:20.52,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,She's doing all the parts!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.92,0:06:23.20,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Go! Run away, quick!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.52,0:06:27.10,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if the wings of my love are torn off,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.10,0:06:29.53,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I shall return to see you...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.88,0:06:37.98,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not a weirdo!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.98,0:06:39.64,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a part-timer! Just a part-timer!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.64,0:06:42.29,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I was making props, see?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.30,0:06:47.61,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,U-Um, look...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.61,0:06:50.80,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know anything about plays,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.80,0:06:54.27,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,but that was pretty great just now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.27,0:06:56.18,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,R-Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.53,0:07:01.19,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,With your skill, they should \Ngive you a better part.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.79,0:07:07.09,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm no good at it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.19,0:07:12.45,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,When I'm in front of people, \NI feel weak at the knees.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.91,0:07:16.45,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I get scared. Everyone's looking at me...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.94,0:07:22.42,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I feel like they see right through me \Nand are ridiculing me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.86,0:07:25.47,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks to that, I keep flubbing lines...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.47,0:07:28.91,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though this is the first time \NI've gotten a role with lines,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.91,0:07:31.74,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a nuisance to everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.74,0:07:35.22,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess I'm really not \Ncut out to be an actress.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.03,0:07:37.79,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,A radish could out-act me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.72,0:07:44.23,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Try a pumpkin.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.15,0:07:47.48,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,P-Pump...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.48,0:07:50.08,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone's like that in the beginning.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.08,0:07:52.99,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But after you get used to it, you don't \Neven notice the eyes of the audience.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.72,0:07:56.57,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's like they say...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.57,0:08:01.25,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Think of the audience as \Nrows of pumpkins in a field.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.07,0:08:06.29,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll try!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.77,0:08:11.50,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,0)}The Next Day
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.50,0:08:14.64,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,Marth and Roza
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.64,0:08:25.77,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What a beautiful theater!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.77,0:08:28.94,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And it's got a retractable roof, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.06,0:08:33.95,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's Tamura-san, the actor!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.17,0:08:37.95,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Look! Anan's here, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.51,0:08:42.20,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow! Celebrities everywhere!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.50,0:08:45.46,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If that girl had this one's personality,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.46,0:08:47.82,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,she wouldn't have any hassles.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.45,0:08:48.46,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}I can't wait, you know, Kaito?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.46,0:08:51.23,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What kind of expression is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.23,0:08:56.22,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You said you wanted to see the play, \Nso I had my dad get us complimentary tickets!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.72,0:08:59.85,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's see a little more \Ngratitude on your face!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.85,0:09:01.85,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.28,0:09:05.10,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Electric room, sound off! Any abnormalities?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.10,0:09:08.36,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The power and wiring are fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.36,0:09:09.89,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Be careful!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.89,0:09:13.36,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Taking advantage of a blackout to \Nsteal is a common tactic of his.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.72,0:09:16.28,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Stay alert!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.28,0:09:16.86,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.96,0:09:23.20,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,All right. At least we won't \Nlose power in the theater.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.20,0:09:25.72,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And even if we do,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.72,0:09:32.21,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,the 20 battery-powered lights we \Nset up will keep him in our sights!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.87,0:09:37.73,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Kid, this is your last appearance.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.73,0:09:42.22,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll never get the chance \Nto escape from me again!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.22,0:09:43.96,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.96,0:09:46.53,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Furuhata Megumi, Furuhata Megumi...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.53,0:09:47.73,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,There!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.41,0:09:51.80,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Furuhata Megumi... "Servant A."
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.35,0:09:56.49,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you laughin' at?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.85,0:09:59.87,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,After all, it's unusual.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.87,0:10:03.24,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That you wanted to see a play like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.08,0:10:06.50,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The setting is Europe in the Middle Ages.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.04,0:10:10.72,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,A prince and princess from two \Ncountries that are enemies
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.72,0:10:14.76,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,overcome various obstacles \Nto be together in the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.28,0:10:17.76,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a totally romantic story.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.27,0:10:19.51,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.51,0:10:23.57,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And now you're embarrassed! How cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.57,0:10:26.02,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I shouldn't have come here with her...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.57,0:10:31.85,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for your patience.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.85,0:10:35.78,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We now present {\i1}Marth and Rosa{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.88,0:10:43.49,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's no use.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.96,0:10:48.75,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I've searched all over the country, but no \Nwoman here would make me a suitable wife.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.34,0:10:52.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't she out there somewhere?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.40,0:10:55.24,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Beautiful, sweet,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.24,0:10:59.81,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,and dazzling like this Green Dream,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.81,0:11:02.51,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,the royal family treasure!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.93,0:11:25.53,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Kid didn't show up.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.53,0:11:31.63,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No, but there's one more scene where the \Njewel's shown, so it'll be out of our hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.63,0:11:34.54,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He'll probably make a play for it then!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.64,0:11:39.80,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,A ball to choose the queen?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.17,0:11:43.80,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh... Hosted by Prince Marth of Gaia...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.80,0:11:47.02,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,D-Don't do it, Princess!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.02,0:11:49.56,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Gaia is our country's enemy!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.56,0:11:52.10,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If you're discovered, \Nwho knows what would happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.98,0:11:54.56,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Megumi-chan's on!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.94,0:11:57.21,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Please think better of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.21,0:12:01.48,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Then are you saying that I, \Nthe most beautiful woman in the world,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.48,0:12:05.07,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,should be shut away in this \Ncountry for the rest of my life?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.58,0:12:11.08,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,U-Um, I-I wasn't saying...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.04,0:12:15.29,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Reiko's suddenly ad-libbing again!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.29,0:12:18.32,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Never mind. You can be excused.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.13,0:12:27.45,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have a good feeling \Nabout that heroine...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.45,0:12:28.81,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.69,0:12:32.31,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What were you thinking?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.31,0:12:34.42,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you want to ruin the show?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.42,0:12:36.81,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,N-No, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.37,0:12:40.32,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You're an eyesore.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.81,0:12:43.70,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Get out of my sight.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.12,0:12:48.20,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Reiko-san! You're on!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.98,0:13:01.71,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have anything to worry about!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.71,0:13:04.41,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not your fault, Megumi!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.41,0:13:06.97,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, cheer up!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.36,0:13:09.66,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's almost the last scene.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.66,0:13:11.31,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go backstage.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.56,0:13:14.83,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.61,0:13:27.82,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, beautiful one!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.32,0:13:31.83,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I hope you will become my wife.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.83,0:13:34.40,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It cannot be, Prince.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.40,0:13:37.48,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,A relationship between us is forbidden.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.70,0:13:43.40,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If you would have it, I would give you...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.54,0:13:49.85,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,...the Gaia royal family's treasure, \NGreen Dream!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.29,0:13:52.35,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, where are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.35,0:13:54.85,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Where are you gonna come from, Kid?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.85,0:13:58.85,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You won't be able to hide \Nin the dark tonight!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.20,0:14:03.10,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You're naive, Inspector.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.10,0:14:07.36,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Darkness isn't the only thing \Nthat can hide a person.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.87,0:14:14.41,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,L-Lights?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.04,0:14:21.69,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Crap!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.77,0:14:33.48,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Th-The jewel!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.10,0:14:37.10,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,The emerald is mine!\N- Kid the Phantom Thief
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.10,0:14:41.56,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You... I didn't think you'd use \Nbright lights to disappear...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.56,0:14:43.62,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up and lock down \Nall entrances and exits!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.62,0:14:45.61,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He's still in the theater!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.18,0:14:48.95,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Inspector! What about the electric room?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.67,0:14:52.95,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Leave it! I want everyone on exits!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.95,0:14:55.45,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9}Electric Room
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.08,0:15:04.81,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What the...?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.81,0:15:06.10,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What's happening?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.88,0:15:13.85,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,After the curtain of night closed in\N and the moon began to tilt,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.85,0:15:17.34,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,there was still one girl in the palace \Nafter everyone had left the ball,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.34,0:15:21.10,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,and she was in love with the prince.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.44,0:15:23.10,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Her name...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.03,0:15:26.11,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,...was Servant A!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.33,0:15:34.70,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,She had been bullied every day\N by the mean princess...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.25,0:15:38.87,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,...and couldn't tell anyone \Nhow she felt.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.87,0:15:42.99,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This lovely girl just \Nendured the pain
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.99,0:15:44.99,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,in her small chest, \Nlike that of a baby bird.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.99,0:15:48.13,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Th-These cheesy lines...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.14,0:16:02.64,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But then a strange magician...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.06,0:16:06.65,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,...appeared from above...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.97,0:16:10.66,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,...and alighted before her.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.61,0:16:16.19,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,K-Kid the Phantom Thief!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.53,0:16:19.37,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,K-Kid?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.27,0:16:23.37,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I'm not Kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.37,0:16:26.22,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm just a magician who'll make...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.64,0:16:30.17,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,...your dream come true!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.82,0:16:37.84,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I stole this jewel, just as I\N stole the light...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.18,0:16:43.18,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,...but it seems it's not \Nwhat I was looking for.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.64,0:16:47.69,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's keep this...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.17,0:16:50.06,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,...on your beautiful finger.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.81,0:16:56.06,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it's time, my lady.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.70,0:16:59.70,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Go to your prince.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.04,0:17:07.46,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,B-But...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.46,0:17:09.79,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But I...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.44,0:17:12.78,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.38,0:17:14.78,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't do this!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.81,0:17:17.97,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Director! Should I lower the curtain?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.97,0:17:20.42,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No, leave it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.94,0:17:23.53,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Pumpkins.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.98,0:17:28.98,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You mustn't escape the audience's gaze.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.74,0:17:32.09,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Muster courage and accept it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.63,0:17:37.28,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No one can see through to your heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.57,0:17:40.35,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.61,0:17:42.68,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.12,0:18:28.70,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,S-She's singing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.70,0:18:30.21,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Megumi!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.65,0:18:57.34,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! What a beautiful singing voice!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.34,0:18:59.40,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It feels as if my mind is clear\N for the first time.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.40,0:19:01.16,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,M-Marth-sama...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.61,0:19:05.16,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Come, let me see your face more clearly.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.84,0:19:07.95,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What a pretty young woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.61,0:19:11.69,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't move...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.65,0:19:16.17,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,...so this moment won't escape me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.70,0:19:26.34,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, let's continue with the play!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.34,0:19:28.68,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes! For Megumi...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.30,0:20:13.02,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't know the story \Nwould be this beautiful!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.02,0:20:15.73,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if that was the real \NKid the Phantom Thief before?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.73,0:20:17.23,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You know, Kaito?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.66,0:20:20.25,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.25,0:20:22.74,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That had to be an actor, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.15,0:20:26.21,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But what a great play!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.21,0:20:29.24,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. I'm glad I got to see it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.63,0:20:32.54,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks, Kaito.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.29,0:20:57.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Inspector, I wonder why Kid \Ndidn't make off with the jewel.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.17,0:20:59.56,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,How would I know?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.65,0:21:12.83,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Megumi-san's in another magazine!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.83,0:21:16.94,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,She been famous ever since that play.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.94,0:21:20.38,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. I hear she's gonna be \Nin a TV drama next.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.38,0:21:23.86,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But there's something \NI don't like about her.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.86,0:21:25.84,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.20,0:21:31.73,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, after all, her ideal man \Nis Kid the Phantom Thief...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.23,0:21:38.66,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,Yoshida Megumi\NExclusive Interview\NMy ideal man is Kid the Phantom Thief
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.84,0:21:36.27,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That sucks!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.64,0:21:45.65,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Tonight, a nameless servant
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.65,0:21:49.02,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,became a dazzling star \Nin the space of a moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.66,0:21:53.08,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone is the main character \Nof their own life.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.08,0:21:55.24,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course, that goes for you, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.00,0:22:00.51,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, see you next illusion.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.44,0:23:33.98,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Boy, Megumi-chan had a \Nbeautiful singing voice!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.98,0:23:36.57,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I wish I could have listened to her \Nforever, but who's got the time?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.57,0:23:38.74,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The next treasure's waiting for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.12,0:23:41.48,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Who's calling me an amateur?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.48,0:23:43.94,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems you've got confidence \Nin your own thieving ability,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.94,0:23:46.11,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,but it wouldn't be wise\N to underestimate me.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.11,0:23:48.11,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I accept your challenge!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.11,0:23:53.24,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time on {\i1}Magic Kaito 1412{\i0}: \NGolden Eye (Part One): Chat Noir's Challenge!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.11,0:23:53.24,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,Golden Eye (Part One):\NChat Noir's Challenge
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.68,0:23:56.58,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Step right this way! Watch carefully!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.58,0:23:58.90,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't miss the illusion!
